Gourmand dreams 🌰 @pistacheskincare 

Pistachio Biscotti Eau de Parfum by Pistache Skincare is a gourmand delight, opening with a strong pistachio. The heart of the fragrance features a warm, buttery biscotti accord, truly capturing the essence of the baked treat.  The base is a sweet and slightly nutty adding depth and warmth. I enjoyed this warm, gourmand scent🤌🤌

The longevity of the fragrance is moderate, lasting for several hours on the skin.

Available @amazon for CAD78.

For the best Pistache Skincare products, be sure to purchase directly from Amazon.com, sold by Pistache Skincare.  This ensures you’re getting authentic products and the best possible experience.
